heading: Kor Valar Ramparts Dungeon Guide
content: Kor Valar Ramparts has the low value , a mediocre layout and is tucked away far from a waypoint, adding travel time to your dungeon completion. Avoid this dungeon if you can, or complete it once for the Renown value only. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
